# Phase-2 deploy env for script/Deploy2.s.sol
# Copy to `.env` and fill one column (production OR §9 rehearsal). Never commit secrets.
#
# Usage:
#   set -a && source .env && set +a
#   forge script script/Deploy2.s.sol:Deploy2 --rpc-url $RPC_URL --broadcast --slow

# =============================================================================
# Wallet / chain
# =============================================================================
# PRIVATE_KEY     deployer EOA (fresh burner for rehearsal; hardware-backed for prod)
# RPC_URL         Robinhood Chain 4663 RPC
PRIVATE_KEY=
RPC_URL=

# =============================================================================
# Core addresses
# PRODUCTION                          | §9 REHEARSAL
# =============================================================================
# SCRATCH         real $SCRATCH       | throwaway ERC-20 from burner deploy
# TREASURY        ops multisig        | rehearsal EOA / temp multisig
SCRATCH=
TREASURY=

# =============================================================================
# StakingVault
# PRODUCTION                          | §9 REHEARSAL
# =============================================================================
# EMISSION_RATE   ~2.31e16 (≈2000 tickets/day vault pool; tune to EV) | high (e.g. 1e18 — ~1 ticket/sec sole staker)
# MIN_STAKE       product threshold (SCRATCH-wei)                    | tiny (e.g. 1e18)
EMISSION_RATE=
MIN_STAKE=

# =============================================================================
# ScratchGame / StandardTicketSource
# PRODUCTION                          | §9 REHEARSAL
# =============================================================================
# RESCUE_DELAY    86400 (24h)         | 600 (10 min)
# PROMO_DAILY_CAP 1000000000000000000000 (1000e18 ticket-wei) | same or lower for rehearsal
RESCUE_DELAY=
PROMO_DAILY_CAP=

# =============================================================================
# Chainlink VRF v2.5 (GATES.md — coordinator on 4663 is an open gate)
# PRODUCTION                          | §9 REHEARSAL
# =============================================================================
# VRF_COORDINATOR live coordinator    | same once known (do not hardcode a placeholder in Solidity)
# VRF_KEYHASH     oracle key hash     | same
# VRF_SUB_ID      funded subscription | rehearsal-funded sub
# VRF_NATIVE_PAYMENT  true on 4663 (ETH gas) for both
VRF_COORDINATOR=
VRF_KEYHASH=
VRF_SUB_ID=
VRF_NATIVE_PAYMENT=true

# =============================================================================
# Prize tables (ABI-encoded ScratchGame.PrizeRow[])
# =============================================================================
# Encoding format:
#   Each table is `abi.encode(PrizeRow[])` where PrizeRow =
#     (address asset, uint96 amountOrBps, bool isBpsOfPool, uint32 cumOdds)
#   Rules (enforced on-chain by ScratchGame.setPrizeTable):
#     - cumOdds strictly increasing
#     - last row MUST be no-win: asset = address(0), cumOdds = 1000000 (1e6)
#   Deploy2 also asserts STANDARD rows are $SCRATCH-only (GATES.md); terminal stays address(0).
#
# Encode with cast (Solidity tuple array syntax), then paste the 0x… hex:
#   cast abi-encode "((address,uint96,bool,uint32)[])" \
#     "[(SCRATCH,1000000000000000000,false,100000),(0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000,0,false,1000000)]"
#
# Example STANDARD ($SCRATCH-only, 10% win 1 SCRATCH / 90% no-win) — substitute real SCRATCH:
#   STANDARD_PRIZE_TABLE=0x…   # encode with SCRATCH address as the only winning asset
#
# Example PREMIUM (may include USDG / other assets once known — GATES.md):
#   PREMIUM_PRIZE_TABLE=0x…    # typically multi-asset; terminal no-win required
#
# PRODUCTION: real odds / EV-tuned tables
# REHEARSAL:   simple high-win tables OK (throwaway token as SCRATCH asset)
PREMIUM_PRIZE_TABLE=
STANDARD_PRIZE_TABLE=

# =============================================================================
# Post-deploy (manual — not in script)
# =============================================================================
# 1. TREASURY must acceptOwnership on: ScratchGame, PrizeVault, StandardTicketSource
#    (addresses printed at end of Deploy2 console output).
# 2. Fund PrizeVault with the 20% seed (treasury multisig tx).
# 3. Add VRF consumer = ChainlinkVRFAdapter on the subscription.
